Package ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.plugin.types

Interface ImyhatTransformer<R>

Type Parameters:
R - the return type to be generated
All Known Subinterfaces:
GenericTransformer<R>
All Known Implementing Classes:
JsonConverter, UnpackJson
public interface ImyhatTransformer<R>
Convert a Shesmu type description into another value

This is meant to transform a description of a Shesmu type into another representation (e.g., a string containing a WDL type)
